user_query: What was the total trading volume for technology stocks last month?
csv_columns: transaction_id, timestamp, customer_id, stock_ticker, quantity, average_trade_size, day_name, is_weekend, is_holiday, stock_liquidity_tier, stock_price, total_trade_amount, transaction_type_BUY, transaction_type_SELL, customer_account_type_Institutional, customer_account_type_Retail, stock_sector_Consumer, stock_sector_Energy, stock_sector_Finance, stock_sector_Healthcare, stock_sector_Technology, stock_industry_Asset Management, stock_industry_Hardware, stock_industry_Oil & Gas, stock_industry_Pharmaceuticals, stock_industry_Renewables, stock_industry_Retail, stock_industry_Software, stock_industry_Utilities
agent_response_sql:
SELECT SUM(quantity) AS total_trading_volume
FROM full_stocks
WHERE stock_sector_Technology = 1 AND timestamp >= DATE('now', '-1 month') AND timestamp < DATE('now')
